Maria Tsien https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Tsien 0 Maria Tsien (also credited as Maria Tsien McClay) was an Asian-American film and television actress in the 1950s and 1960s. She was often cast in productions that were set in Asia, to fill out non-Asian casts.
